<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>MEP Service Contract</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      margin: 40px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1, h2 {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .section {
      margin-top: 25px;
    }
    .box {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .signature {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 80px;
    }
    .sign-box {
      width: 45%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .line {
      margin-top: 60px;
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>MEP Services Agreement</h1>

<p>
This agreement is made on <strong>{{contractDate}}</strong> between:
</p>

<div class="box">
  <p><strong>Client:</strong> {{clientName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{companyName}}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>1. Scope of MEP Services</h2>
  <p>
    The company shall provide Mechanical, Electrical, and Plumbing (MEP) services including:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Electrical system installation and maintenance</li>
    <li>Plumbing and water supply systems</li>
    <li>HVAC installation and servicing</li>
    <li>Testing, commissioning, and documentation</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>2. Project Details</h2>
  <p><strong>Project Location:</strong> {{projectLocation}}</p>
  <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</p>
  <p><strong>End Date:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>3. Payment Terms</h2>
  <p>Total Contract Amount: <strong>Rs. {{amount}}</strong></p>
  <p>Payment shall be released based on agreed milestones.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>4. Terms & Conditions</h2>
  <p>
    The company agrees to follow all applicable safety standards, building codes,
    and Nepal government regulations.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="signature">
  <div class="sign-box">
    <div class="line"></div>
    <p><strong>{{clientName}}</strong></p>
    <p>Client Signature</p>
  </div>

  <div class="sign-box">
    <div class="line"></div>
    <p><strong>{{companyName}}</strong></p>
    <p>Company Signature</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
